{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm a filmmaker."},{"time":2000,"text":"For the last 8 years,"},{"time":4000,"text":"I have dedicated my life"},{"time":6000,"text":"to documenting the work"},{"time":8000,"text":"of Israelis and Palestinians"},{"time":10000,"text":"who are trying to end the conflict"},{"time":12000,"text":"using peaceful means."},{"time":14000,"text":"When I travel with my work"},{"time":16000,"text":"across Europe and the United States,"},{"time":18000,"text":"one question always comes up:"},{"time":23000,"text":"Where is the Palestinian Gandhi?"},{"time":25000,"text":"Why aren't Palestinians"},{"time":27000,"text":"using nonviolent resistance?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"The challenge I face when I hear this question"},{"time":33000,"text":"is that often I have just returned from the Middle East"},{"time":36000,"text":"where I spent my time"},{"time":38000,"text":"filming dozens of Palestinians"},{"time":40000,"text":"who are using nonviolence"},{"time":42000,"text":"to defend their lands"},{"time":44000,"text":"and water resources"},{"time":46000,"text":"from Israeli soldiers and settlers."},{"time":49000,"text":"These leaders are trying to forge"},{"time":52000,"text":"a massive national nonviolent movement"},{"time":55000,"text":"to end the occupation"},{"time":57000,"text":"and build peace in the region."},{"time":59000,"text":"Yet, most of you"},{"time":61000,"text":"have probably never heard about them."},{"time":64000,"text":"This divide between what's happening on the ground"},{"time":66000,"text":"and perceptions abroad"},{"time":68000,"text":"is one of the key reasons"},{"time":70000,"text":"why we don't have yet"},{"time":72000,"text":"a Palestinian peaceful resistance movement"},{"time":75000,"text":"that has been successful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"So I'm here today"},{"time":80000,"text":"to talk about the power of attention,"},{"time":82000,"text":"the power of your attention,"},{"time":85000,"text":"and the emergence and development"},{"time":87000,"text":"of nonviolent movements"},{"time":89000,"text":"in the West Bank, Gaza and elsewhere --"},{"time":92000,"text":"but today, my case study is going to be Palestine."},{"time":96000,"text":"I believe that what's mostly missing"},{"time":98000,"text":"for nonviolence to grow"},{"time":100000,"text":"is not for Palestinians"},{"time":102000,"text":"to start adopting nonviolence,"},{"time":105000,"text":"but for us to start paying attention"},{"time":108000,"text":"to those who already are."},{"time":112000,"text":"Allow me to illustrate this point"},{"time":114000,"text":"by taking you to this village"},{"time":116000,"text":"called Budrus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118000,"text":"About seven years ago,"},{"time":120000,"text":"they faced extinction,"},{"time":122000,"text":"because Israel announced it would build a separation barrier,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and part of this barrier"},{"time":126000,"text":"would be built on top of the village."},{"time":128000,"text":"They would lose 40 percent of their land"},{"time":130000,"text":"and be surrounded,"},{"time":132000,"text":"so they would lose free access"},{"time":134000,"text":"to the rest of the West Bank."},{"time":136000,"text":"Through inspired local leadership,"},{"time":138000,"text":"they launched a peaceful resistance campaign"},{"time":141000,"text":"to stop that from happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"Let me show you some brief clips,"},{"time":145000,"text":"so you have a sense"},{"time":147000,"text":"for what that actually looked like on the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156000,"text":"Palestinian Woman: We were told the wall"},{"time":159000,"text":"would separate Palestine from Israel."},{"time":162000,"text":"Here in Budrus,"},{"time":164000,"text":"we realized the wall would steal our land."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"Israeli Man: The fence has, in fact,"},{"time":168000,"text":"created a solution to terror."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"Man: Today you're invited"},{"time":174000,"text":"to a peaceful march."},{"time":180000,"text":"You are joined"},{"time":183000,"text":"by dozens of your Israeli brothers and sisters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"Israeli Activist: Nothing scares the army"},{"time":188000,"text":"more than nonviolent opposition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"Woman: We saw the men"},{"time":195000,"text":"trying to push the soldiers,"},{"time":197000,"text":"but none of them could do that."},{"time":200000,"text":"But I think the girls could do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"Fatah Party Member: We must empty our minds"},{"time":210000,"text":"of traditional thinking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"Hamas Party Member: We were in complete harmony,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and we wanted to spread it to all of Palestine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"Chanting: One united nation."},{"time":223000,"text":"Fatah, Hamas and the Popular Front!"},{"time":227000,"text":"News Anchor: The clashes over the fence continue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229000,"text":"Reporter: Israeli border police were sent to disperse the crowd."},{"time":233000,"text":"They were allowed to use any force necessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"(Gunshots)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"Man: These are live bullets."},{"time":239000,"text":"It's like Fallujah. Shooting everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"Israeli Activist: I was sure we were all going to die."},{"time":245000,"text":"But there were others around me who weren't even cowering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253000,"text":"Israeli Soldier: A nonviolent protest"},{"time":255000,"text":"is not going to stop the [unclear]."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"Protester: This is a peaceful march."},{"time":260000,"text":"There is no need to use violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"Chanting: We can do it! We can do it!"},{"time":267000,"text":"We can do it!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"Julia Bacha: When I first heard"},{"time":273000,"text":"about the story of Budrus,"},{"time":275000,"text":"I was surprised"},{"time":277000,"text":"that the international media had failed to cover"},{"time":280000,"text":"the extraordinary set of events"},{"time":282000,"text":"that happened seven years ago,"},{"time":284000,"text":"in 2003."},{"time":286000,"text":"What was even more surprising"},{"time":288000,"text":"was the fact that Budrus was successful."},{"time":291000,"text":"The residents, after 10 months of peaceful resistance,"},{"time":294000,"text":"convinced the Israeli government"},{"time":297000,"text":"to move the route of the barrier off their lands"},{"time":300000,"text":"and to the green line,"},{"time":302000,"text":"which is the internationally recognized boundary"},{"time":305000,"text":"between Israel and the Palestinian Territories."},{"time":308000,"text":"The resistance in Budrus"},{"time":310000,"text":"has since spread"},{"time":312000,"text":"to villages across the West Bank"},{"time":314000,"text":"and to Palestinian neighborhoods in Jerusalem."},{"time":318000,"text":"Yet the media remains mostly silent"},{"time":321000,"text":"on these stories."},{"time":324000,"text":"This silence carries profound consequences"},{"time":327000,"text":"for the likelihood"},{"time":329000,"text":"that nonviolence can grow,"},{"time":331000,"text":"or even survive,"},{"time":333000,"text":"in Palestine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335000,"text":"Violent resistance"},{"time":337000,"text":"and nonviolent resistance"},{"time":339000,"text":"share one very important thing in common;"},{"time":343000,"text":"they are both a form of theater"},{"time":346000,"text":"seeking an audience to their cause."},{"time":349000,"text":"If violent actors"},{"time":351000,"text":"are the only ones constantly getting front-page covers"},{"time":354000,"text":"and attracting international attention"},{"time":356000,"text":"to the Palestinian issue,"},{"time":358000,"text":"it becomes very hard"},{"time":360000,"text":"for nonviolent leaders"},{"time":362000,"text":"to make the case to their communities"},{"time":364000,"text":"that civil disobedience"},{"time":366000,"text":"is a viable option"},{"time":368000,"text":"in addressing their plight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"The power of attention"},{"time":372000,"text":"is probably going to come as no surprise"},{"time":374000,"text":"to the parents in the room."},{"time":377000,"text":"The surest way"},{"time":379000,"text":"to make your child throw increasingly louder tantrums"},{"time":382000,"text":"is by giving him attention"},{"time":384000,"text":"the first time he throws a fit."},{"time":386000,"text":"The tantrum will become"},{"time":388000,"text":"what childhood psychologists call"},{"time":390000,"text":"a functional behavior,"},{"time":392000,"text":"since the child has learned"},{"time":394000,"text":"that he can get parental attention out of it."},{"time":398000,"text":"Parents can incentivize or disincentivize behavior"},{"time":402000,"text":"simply by giving or withdrawing"},{"time":404000,"text":"attention to their children."},{"time":407000,"text":"But that's true for adults too."},{"time":410000,"text":"In fact, the behavior"},{"time":412000,"text":"of entire communities and countries"},{"time":414000,"text":"can be influenced,"},{"time":416000,"text":"depending on where"},{"time":418000,"text":"the international community chooses"},{"time":420000,"text":"to focus its attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"I believe that at the core of ending the conflict in the Middle East"},{"time":427000,"text":"and bringing peace"},{"time":429000,"text":"is for us"},{"time":431000,"text":"to transform nonviolence"},{"time":433000,"text":"into a functional behavior"},{"time":435000,"text":"by giving a lot more attention"},{"time":437000,"text":"to the nonviolent leaders on the ground today."},{"time":441000,"text":"In the course of taking my film to villages"},{"time":444000,"text":"in the West Bank, in Gaza and in East Jerusalem,"},{"time":447000,"text":"I have seen the impact"},{"time":449000,"text":"that even one documentary film can have"},{"time":452000,"text":"in influencing the transformation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"In a village called Wallajeh,"},{"time":458000,"text":"which sits very close to Jerusalem,"},{"time":461000,"text":"the community was facing"},{"time":463000,"text":"a very similar plight to Budrus."},{"time":465000,"text":"They were going to be surrounded, lose a lot of their lands"},{"time":468000,"text":"and not have freedom of access,"},{"time":470000,"text":"either to the West Bank or Jerusalem."},{"time":473000,"text":"They had been using nonviolence for about two years"},{"time":476000,"text":"but had grown disenchanted"},{"time":478000,"text":"since nobody was paying attention."},{"time":481000,"text":"So we organized a screening."},{"time":484000,"text":"A week later,"},{"time":486000,"text":"they held the most well-attended"},{"time":488000,"text":"and disciplined"},{"time":490000,"text":"demonstration to date."},{"time":493000,"text":"The organizers say"},{"time":495000,"text":"that the villagers, upon seeing the story of Budrus"},{"time":497000,"text":"documented in a film,"},{"time":499000,"text":"felt that there were indeed people"},{"time":501000,"text":"following what they were doing,"},{"time":503000,"text":"that people cared."},{"time":505000,"text":"So they kept on going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507000,"text":"On the Israeli side,"},{"time":509000,"text":"there is a new peace movement called Solidariot,"},{"time":512000,"text":"which means solidarity in Hebrew."},{"time":515000,"text":"The leaders of this movement have been using Budrus"},{"time":518000,"text":"as one of their primary recruiting tools."},{"time":521000,"text":"They report"},{"time":523000,"text":"that Israelis who had never been active before,"},{"time":525000,"text":"upon seeing the film,"},{"time":527000,"text":"understand the power of nonviolence"},{"time":529000,"text":"and start joining their activities."},{"time":531000,"text":"The examples of Wallajeh"},{"time":533000,"text":"and the Solidariot movement"},{"time":535000,"text":"show that even a small-budget independent film"},{"time":539000,"text":"can play a role"},{"time":541000,"text":"in transforming nonviolence"},{"time":543000,"text":"into a functional behavior."},{"time":546000,"text":"Now imagine the power"},{"time":548000,"text":"that big media players could have"},{"time":551000,"text":"if they started covering"},{"time":553000,"text":"the weekly nonviolent demonstrations"},{"time":555000,"text":"happening in villages"},{"time":557000,"text":"like Bil'in, Ni'lin,"},{"time":559000,"text":"Wallajeh,"},{"time":561000,"text":"in Jerusalem neighborhoods"},{"time":563000,"text":"like Sheikh Jarrah and Silwan --"},{"time":566000,"text":"the nonviolent leaders"},{"time":568000,"text":"would become more visible,"},{"time":570000,"text":"valued and effective"},{"time":572000,"text":"in their work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575000,"text":"I believe"},{"time":577000,"text":"that the most important thing"},{"time":579000,"text":"is to understand"},{"time":581000,"text":"that if we don't pay attention to these efforts,"},{"time":584000,"text":"they are invisible,"},{"time":586000,"text":"and it's as if they never happened."},{"time":588000,"text":"But I have seen first hand"},{"time":590000,"text":"that if we do,"},{"time":592000,"text":"they will multiply."},{"time":594000,"text":"If they multiply,"},{"time":596000,"text":"their influence will grow"},{"time":598000,"text":"in the overall Israeli-Palestinian conflict."},{"time":600000,"text":"And theirs is the kind of influence"},{"time":603000,"text":"that can finally"},{"time":605000,"text":"unblock the situation."},{"time":607000,"text":"These leaders have proven that nonviolence works"},{"time":610000,"text":"in places like Budrus."},{"time":612000,"text":"Let's give them attention"},{"time":614000,"text":"so they can prove it works everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}